Package aspguidp.service.core.asp.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DlvAnswerSetManager
    Implementation of the AnswerSetManager interface which extracts answer sets from the output of the dlv logic program solver.
    DlvAspSolverService
    Implementation of the AspSolverService interface which implements the execution of the dlv logic program solver.
    DlvSolverMessageManager
    Implementation of the SolverMessageManager interface which extracts messages from the output of the dlv logic program solver.
